<text top="246" left="57" width="61" height="13" font="0">Agenda item 3 </text>
<text top="262" left="57" width="222" height="9" font="2"><b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil, </b></text>
<text top="274" left="57" width="196" height="9" font="2"><b>political, economic, social and cultural rights, </b></text>
<text top="286" left="57" width="150" height="9" font="2"><b>including the right to development </b></text>
<text top="309" left="57" width="2" height="9" font="2"><b> </b></text>
<text top="309" left="99" width="2" height="9" font="2"><b> </b></text>
